Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,(藤森裡穗)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了\N回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你回來了啊\N我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小純怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一會慢慢聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小純那個傢伙還很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好像辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,從交通事故依賴\N還沒振作起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都過了一年了\N還沒好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你對他瞭解嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也不只是夫人去世的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可能工作還有身體什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，好把心他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真想幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他父母從我小時候就照顴我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我很嘹解他的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候暑假\N我常去小純家裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可能現在最好的\N是換個環境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要他來我家住段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?\N當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人都是太寂寞了才生病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯的建議\N我讓他來這邊找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（老公，請原諒我!）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小純
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,之前很感謝你來\N小純好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,海美，好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別傻站著了\N先進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,講進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,請用吧\N不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來你家打擾\N我們很期待你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的家有點小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想著房子建好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,請你來家裡玩\N好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在東京有這麼好的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,和我完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也奮鬥了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還沒小孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,正想著要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小純，還是沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子去世之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就不知道自己活著的意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,人就是覺得自己為了誰活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,才努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明天還要早起吧\N睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N為難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,早安\N去工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今天她也要去打工\N早飯做好了，你自己吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走了\N再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上主要吃咖喱還是燉飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,將太對好說我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,將太?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一直說很吃駑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,將太不是那麼冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,傷害我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為妻子去世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她自己出軌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,去見男人的時候\N中途被車撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,將太不會懂吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,海美你也是\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,會是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛我是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我，請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛我\N冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道背叛我\N是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我是什麼心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，小純，冷靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點\N我搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公之外的男人做這樣的事情\N是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以，那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,做那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，來你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N我很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，停下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了，那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣我很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,射了射了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是來了啊\N再做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,海美呢\N去洗澡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就做好了\N將太要吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像有精神多了\N好開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這個，端過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小純開朗多了\N多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒做什麼\N謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼心情?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛我出軌\N是什麼心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小純 放開我\N請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再見 加油哦\N謝謝 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,慢一點，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，不要繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷淡啊\N不擔心我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，等一下\N請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,用行動證明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好好含住，幫我爽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.03,0:25:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.64,0:26:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.52,0:26:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,海美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.92,0:26:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不在家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.99,0:26:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我放到門口了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.43,0:29:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,東京的就職機會好多
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.03,0:29:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼工怍好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.91,0:29:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不能總住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.31,0:29:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也會給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.51,0:29:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不用介意\N將來那是做嬰兒房
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.92,0:29:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嬰兒房?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.32,0:29:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還說沒有計劃\N難道在要小孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.46,0:30:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有\N還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.20,0:30:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喝過酒困了\N我先去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.14,0:30:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,海美，晚安\N晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.42,0:30:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.35,0:30:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.09,0:30:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的明天再冼吧\N趕快來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.66,0:31:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，將太
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.40,0:31:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事\N我說了這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.07,0:31:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那個傢伙\N已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.61,0:31:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.82,0:31:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是為了讓我好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.36,0:31:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要協助我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.63,0:31:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.37,0:31:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.91,0:32:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,其實很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.40,0:32:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不安靜一點  他會起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:33:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.12,0:33:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,停下來\N喜歡這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.79,0:33:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.82,0:33:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.49,0:34:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞\N真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.84,0:35:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.38,0:35:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.74,0:35:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.00,0:36:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.38,0:37:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,下麵很濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.92,0:37:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.05,0:37:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎?
